<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">无将大车</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson13d559f0f799">
<p>无将大车，祇自尘兮。无思百忧，祇自疧兮。</p>
<p>无将大车，维尘冥冥。无思百忧，不出于颎。</p>
<p>无将大车，维尘雍兮。无思百忧，祇自重兮。</p>
</div>
</div>
